OL,3,CChancellor's spending review
OL,4,Cchallenges youth violence goals,
OL,5,Cpolice chief warns
OL,7,FThere will be 'further challenges' for
OL,8,FWest Midlands Police as a result of
OL,9,Fthe Chancellor's Spending Review,
OL,10,Faccording to its Police and Crime
OL,11,FCommissioner.
OL,13,FLabour's Simon Foster told ITV News
OL,14,FCentral: "There's no doubt that this
OL,15,Fspending review announcement is going
OL,16,Fto provide yet further challenges for
OL,17,FWest Midlands Police.
