OL,3,CChancellor's spending review
OL,4,Cchallenges youth violence goals,
OL,5,Cpolice chief warns
OL,7,F"Particularly if we're going to
OL,8,Fdeliver on the government's National
OL,9,FNeighbourhood Policing guarantee, its
OL,10,Fcommitments around halving violence
OL,11,Fagainst women and girls and its
OL,12,Fcommitment to halve youth violence and
OL,13,Fknife crime"
OL,15,FFoster had called for the chancellor
OL,16,Fto return 700 West Midlands Police
OL,17,Fofficers the region has lost since
OL,18,F2010. He now admits that it won't
OL,19,Fhappen, despite securing an additional
OL,20,F150 neighbourhood officers for the
OL,21,Fregion.
