OL,7,FSpeaking before the spending review,
OL,8,Fhe said: "The people of the West
OL,9,FMidlands have been short-changed for
OL,10,Ffar too long.
OL,12,F"We still have nearly 700 fewer police
OL,13,Fofficers than in 2010, despite rising
OL,14,Fdemand and increasing complexity in
OL,15,Fthe nature of crime.
OL,17,F"However, many other police force
OL,18,Fareas now have more police officers
OL,19,Fthan they have ever had in their force
OL,20,Fhistories.
