OL,3,CChancellor's spending review
OL,4,Cchallenges youth violence goals,
OL,5,Cpolice chief warns
OL,7,F"That is not fair and it is not just.
OL,8,FThe West Midlands has been
OL,9,Fshortchanged for far too long. It's
OL,10,Ftime for the Government to take this
OL,11,Fopportunity to put that right."
OL,13,FPolice funding in England and Wales is
OL,14,Fset to rise by 2.3% in real terms each
OL,15,Fyear, a figure that falls short of
OL,16,Fwhat many police bosses say is really
OL,17,Fneeded.
