OL,3,CChancellor's spending review
OL,4,Cchallenges youth violence goals,
OL,5,Cpolice chief warns
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves claimed the
OL,8,Fadditional funding, totalling more
OL,9,Fthan #2 billion, would be enough to
OL,10,Fmeet headline government promises on
OL,11,Ftackling crime and maintaining police
OL,12,Fnumbers.
OL,14,FHowever, those sums are being met with
OL,15,Fscepticism, with the wider Home Office
OL,16,Fbudget set to shrink by 1.7% a year.
OL,18,FFoster said he wants a 'fairer funding
OL,19,Fformula' that allocates resources
OL,20,Fbased on demand and need, rather than
OL,21,Fmetrics that disadvantage urban areas.
