OL,3,CChancellor's spending review
OL,4,Cchallenges youth violence goals,
OL,5,Cpolice chief warns
OL,7,FHe said: "We need a funding model that
OL,8,Freflects the real pressures on
OL,9,Fpolicing in our region," he added.
OL,10,F"The current formula is broken and
OL,11,Funfit for purpose. It fails to account
OL,12,Ffor the scale of demand we face, from
OL,13,Fserious organised crime to
OL,14,Fsafeguarding vulnerable people.
OL,16,F"This is not about more money. It is
OL,17,Fabout delivering a fairer allocation
OL,18,Fof funding, to keep our people and
OL,19,Fcommunities safe and secure."
